info.author: Techin Alex Kang
info.description:
Functional and API tempest tests for openstack project vmware-nsx.
This project is implemented using openstack tempest external plugin allowing users to execute tempest tests from tempest directory.

The major functions to be managed by this project are neutron specific functions, for example l2gw, lbaas that upstream tempest are no longer supported and should be moved to neutron project.
info.name: vmware-nsx-tempest
info.summary: StackForge project of openstack project vmware-nsx hosting vmware-nsx specific neutron tests
